flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Read DB Schema"]
    B --> C["Generate SQL<br/>from NL Question"]
    C --> D["Execute SQL<br/>against SQLite"]
    D --> E{Execution OK?}
    E -->|Yes| F["Return Results"]
    E -->|No| G{Max Attempts<br/>Reached?}
    G -->|No| H["LLM Debug:<br/>Fix SQL Error"]
    H --> D
    G -->|Yes| I["Surface Failure<br/>to Caller"]
    F --> J([End])
    I --> J